# KOMPLETE-KONTROL CLI - The Ultimate Agentic Coding Tool

**Command**: `komplete` (or `kk` for short)
**Timeline**: 8 weeks
**Budget**: ~$35K development + $140-725/month operational

---

## üöÄ Quick Overview

KOMPLETE-KONTROL is a production-ready CLI tool that combines **AI intelligence**, **reverse engineering**, and **multi-agent capabilities** to create the absolute best agentic coding tool.

---

## ‚ú® Core Features

### 1. **Easy Model Switching** (Week 2)
- **Prefix-based routing**: `g/gemini-3-pro`, `oai/gpt-5.2`, `fl/llama-3.1-70b-abliterated`
- **7+ providers**: Anthropic, OpenAI, Gemini, OpenRouter, Ollama, Groq, Featherless
- **Fallback chain**: Automatic failover if primary model fails
- **Abliterated models**: Uncensored models via Featherless.ai

### 2. **Auto-Context Condensing** (Week 2)
- **Smart threshold**: Triggers at 40% (configurable 20-80%)
- **Intelligent summarization**: Uses fast model (Haiku, GPT-4o-mini)
- **Preserves tool calls**: Never loses function call history
- **Hybrid fallback**: Sliding window if condensation fails

### 3. **TRUE Parallel Agents** (Week 3-4)
- **2-100+ agents**: LangGraph supervisor-worker pattern
- **Git worktrees**: Conflict-free filesystem isolation
- **16 specializations**: Frontend, Backend, Security, Performance, DevOps, etc.
- **3 pre-built patterns**: Code Review, Full-Stack Build, Test Migration
- **Real-time monitoring**: Live dashboard with token/cost tracking

### 4. **Reverse Engineering Suite** (Week 5)
- **Frida** (‚úÖ installed): Dynamic instrumentation, SSL pinning bypass
- **mitmproxy** (‚úÖ installed): HTTP/HTTPS interception, API discovery
- **JADX**: APK decompilation, secret detection
- **GraphQL/gRPC**: Introspection and fuzzing
- **Binary analysis**: Ghidra integration ready

### 5. **Self-Healing Infrastructure** (Week 6)
- **Predictive failure detection**: AI predicts crashes 5-30 minutes ahead
- **Auto-recovery**: Restart, scale up, or rollback automatically
- **Health monitoring**: Track CPU, memory, response times
- **Zero-downtime**: Prevent failures before they occur

### 6. **Deep Research** (Week 6)
- **Perplexity Sonar**: Real-time web search with citations
- **Tavily API**: Research-grade LLM-optimized results
- **arXiv**: 2.3M scientific papers (FREE)
- **Semantic Scholar**: 200M papers with citations (FREE)
- **255 lines of code ready** to copy

### 7. **RAG Codebase Indexing** (Week 6-7)
- **ChromaDB**: Local vector database (FREE)
- **Semantic search**: Natural language codebase queries
- **Incremental updates**: File watcher for changes
- **216 lines of code ready** to copy

### 8. **Voice-to-Code** (Week 6)
- **Groq Whisper**: 99% accurate transcription
- **Streaming audio**: Real-time processing
- **Context-aware**: Generates code from voice
- **200 lines of code ready** to copy

### 9. **Screenshot-to-Code** (Week 6)
- **GPT-4 Vision**: Analyze UI components
- **React + Tailwind**: Generate production code
- **Puppeteer**: Automated screenshot capture

### 10. **Tech Stack Detection** (Week 6)
- **Framework detection**: React, Vue, Angular, Next.js
- **Backend inference**: Node, Django, Rails
- **CDN & hosting**: Cloudflare, Vercel, AWS
- **370 lines of code ready** to copy

### 11. **Session Management** (Week 7)
- **SQLite persistence**: Resume conversations exactly
- **Knowledge tracking**: Remember architectural decisions
- **Export/import**: Share sessions with team
- **Auto-prune**: Clean up old sessions

### 12. **MCP Server Orchestration**
- **24+ servers available**: PostgreSQL, Semgrep, Playwright, GitHub, etc.
- **Auto-discovery**: Detect installed tools
- **Connection pooling**: Load-balanced requests
- **Custom servers**: Build your own for any tool

