## üéØ Commands

```bash
# Chat & Tasks
komplete chat [--model g/gemini-3-pro]  # Interactive REPL
komplete task "<task>"                  # One-shot execution

# Multi-Agent Swarms
komplete swarm "<task>" --agents 5      # Spawn 5 agents
komplete swarm --pattern code-review    # Pre-built patterns
kk swarm "task" --agents 10            # Short form

# Reverse Engineering
komplete frida attach <pid>             # Dynamic instrumentation
komplete proxy start --port 8080        # Network interception
komplete analyze apk <file>             # Decompile Android APK

# AI Research
komplete research "<query>"             # Deep research
komplete rag ask "<question>"           # Query codebase
komplete voice start                    # Voice-to-code mode
komplete clone-ui <url>                 # Screenshot-to-code

# Self-Healing
komplete heal monitor <service>         # Health monitoring
komplete heal enable <service> --auto   # Auto-recovery
komplete heal status                    # View health status

# Session Management
komplete session list                   # List all sessions
komplete session resume <name>          # Resume session
kk session resume <name>                # Short form

# Model Management
komplete models                         # List all models
komplete models --search "gemini"       # Search models
komplete config --show                  # Show configuration
```

