## üöÄ Quick Start

```bash
# 1. Navigate to project
cd ~/Desktop/Projects/komplete-kontrol-cli

# 2. Install dependencies
bun install

# 3. Set up environment
cp .env.example .env
# Add API keys (ANTHROPIC_API_KEY, OPENAI_API_KEY, etc.)

# 4. Start services
docker run -d -p 8000:8000 chromadb/chroma  # ChromaDB
brew services start redis                    # Redis

# 5. Configure MCP servers
mkdir -p ~/.komplete
# Create ~/.komplete/mcp.json (see docs/IMPLEMENTATION_PLAN.md)

# 6. Build and link
bun run build
npm link

# 7. Test
komplete --version
komplete models
kk chat
```

